<div class="thumbinner" style="width:252px;"><a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:Snake_warning_sign.jpg" class="image"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/7/7f/Snake_warning_sign.jpg/250px-Snake_warning_sign.jpg" width="250" height="362" class="thumbimage" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/7/7f/Snake_warning_sign.jpg/375px-Snake_warning_sign.jpg 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/7/7f/Snake_warning_sign.jpg/500px-Snake_warning_sign.jpg 2x" /></a>
